'''Clan Kihm'bar''' was a [[Noghri/Legends|Noghri]] clan. Notable members of clan Kihm'bar were [[Khabarakh]], who helped free his people from the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Empire's]] [[Slavery/Legends|slavery]], and [[Kahr'corvh]], representative to the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]].

